assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Nakabohtec Corrosion Protecting Co.,Ltd. provides survey, analysis, design, engineering, work supervision, and material supply services for protecting metallic structures from corrosion in Japan. The company is involved in the anti-corrosion business, such as cathodic protection work, painting work, coating anti-corrosion work, and corrosive environment survey and related business; and construction business, including civil engineering work, electrical work, scaffolding work, steel structure work, pavement work, dredging work, waterproofing work, and water supply facility work. The company was formerly known as Nakagawa corrosion Industrial Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Nakabohtec Corrosion Protecting Co.,Ltd. in 1991. Nakabohtec Corrosion Protecting Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1951 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
